channel.title: Loading title screen 0% help!
channel.description: Me, yet again!, with my loading screen stuck on 0% as usual(seems spelled wrong) I try to fix myself before asking. I tried changing my location of my cache and changing my Cache constants to where is was in source folder.... I also tried changing it to be in just my c:\ or if it was c:\revengescapecache Yes it is a revengescape cache... I compiled and got 4 errors and 2 errors on my client compiler... I am running jdk version 1.6.0_25 and my computer is running windows xp Thanks for your time
